Package org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.opensurvey.measurements

package org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.opensurvey.measurements
These beans describe the typical measurements to capture for different types of technologies. They are used to create the JSON for the jsonProperties attribute of the annotation.
